:"2018-08-13T15:16:49.000Z","msg":"甜完仔有肉感 結左婚都仲咁淫<br />\n呢啲成日誘惑人既賤女人一定要好好教訓下<br />\n起勢咁聞佢對大肉腳啲香味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再含佢腳趾舔佢腳板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最好就一一邊踩住我臉一邊囂張咁屌我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用碌鳩頂佢腳板底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個大屁股，淫奶又大又白 格肋底又滑又香 質個頭入去索 舔到佢啲淫肉全部都係口水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用佢對淫奶同大臀肉打我臉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用碌鳩打磨拍佢塊淫臉+奶 令佢成身都充滿住碌鳩嘅雄性味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用兩塊大臀肉同大淫奶玩臀交同夾腸同腋交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n狗仔式打屁股一邊打一邊問喺咪淫婦喺咪成日故意露奶誘惑人屌佢 再屌到佢叫老公 邊問邊大大力打佢個大屁股 再屌到佢個大屁股搖黎搖去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n女下男上張腿當打椿機咁屌 最好屌一下啲淫水擠一大堆出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n從佢背後用手托開對淫腳令佢正面咁屌 等佢自己睇睇下啲淫水幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中出之餘一定要射到佢成身都係精 再用有殘餘精液嘅大龜頭拍佢臉+磨嘴唇<br />\n最後塞入口等佢舔乾淨 令佢變成性奴液便器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f454688bdc1ef01b4638c9fd62388aba8c951c0","tid":777934,"uid":30186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T16:01:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d2fe7e158d45d8d90bc204eae488eda07ee30de","tid":777934,"uid":17889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T16:05:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e83aa4bbb8634b17b862002636ba98ffbfb4ae69","tid":777934,"uid":199456,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T16:12:10.000Z","msg":"一諗起呢一世自己都唔會有呢種囡 就覺得好悲哀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f174c73ba110650f76994fcbaa6128cbd744bbb0","tid":777934,"uid":79451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T16:16:23.000Z","msg":"Milf<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b6c8c77c08499bb0f76a8b37c950d1bc6a1ea22","tid":777934,"uid":84524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T16:24:09.000Z","msg":"個仔大個咗會唔會拎返啲屋企相J自己阿媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <strong></strong>"},{"pid":"1584208d3df68b6798d7d44a3a0533e2d36997e7","tid":777934,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T16:36:37.000Z","msg":"1"}]}